IDL> sciamachy_global_topography, "SCI_SF2_AX-file"

    Shows world height-map contained in the SCI_SF2_AX file.

IDL> sciamachy_mpi_climatology, "SCI_PR2_AX-file"

    Shows a succession of temperature profiles contained in the SCI_PR2_AX file.

IDL> sciamachy_sun_reference, "SCI_NL__1P-file"

    Shows the sun reference spectra as contained in the Level-1b product file.

IDL> sciamachy_level_1b, "SCI_NL__1P-file"

    Shows the complicated level-1b product, pixel readouts.

IDL> sciamachy_level_2, "SCI_NL__2P-directory"

    Shows all nadir ground pixels in the product files, coloured by the
    vertical colomn density of the DOAS_0_O3 retrieval value.

    NOTE: this procedure takes a directory argument, instead of a file, and
           will process all SCI_NL__2P files contained therein.

